            <div corresp="#c3884f2">
                <head>Santiago, Chile</head>
                <p>Franklin B. Atwood detailed to Embassy, Santiago, as a Foreign Service off. for
                    temp. duty, Jan. 19, 1945.</p>
                <p>John B. Taust assigned to Dept. of State temporarily, Nov. 7, 1938.</p>
                <p>H. Coit M. Lean designated Commercial Attaché, April 8, 1944.</p>
